OL,3,CTeachers and pupils react to under-16s
OL,4,Csocial media ban
OL,6,FCumbrian school pupils have reacted to
OL,7,Fthe Prime Minister's announcement that
OL,8,Funder-16s will be banned from using a
OL,9,Fnumber of social media apps.
OL,11,FSnapchat, TikTok and YouTube are among
OL,12,Fthe social media platforms to be made
OL,13,Funavailable to the teenagers by law.
OL,15,FITV Border spoke to students and the
OL,16,Fheadteacher of Penrith's Queen
OL,17,FElizabeth Grammar School to hear their
OL,18,Fopinions on the proposals.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,330,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F329A1781799074
OL,3,CTeachers and pupils react to under-16s
OL,4,Csocial media ban
OL,6,FAdam Marchant, a student in Year 10,
OL,7,Fsaid: "I think (the ban is) both good
OL,8,Fand bad. Some of the platforms being
OL,9,Fbanned, I find them a little bit...
OL,10,Fthey're a bit too much.
OL,12,F"But with YouTube, I use it quite a
OL,13,Flot - for entertainment, but also out
OL,14,Fof interest - there's lots of
OL,15,Fmathematics and science videos that I
OL,16,Fenjoy watching and learn lots from.
OL,26,@oD@PpmoD@[pn
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,330,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F329A1781799074
OL,3,CTeachers and pupils react to under-16s
OL,4,Csocial media ban
OL,6,F"There are so many niches you can find
OL,7,Fon the internet, and connect with a
OL,8,Fcommunity. Things like using graphs to
OL,9,Fcreate images really interest me, and
OL,10,FI wouldn't have discovered that
OL,11,Fwithout social media.
OL,13,F"So it's really getting that balance
OL,14,Fbetween protecting kids, and making
OL,15,Fsure there isn't any harm coming from
OL,16,Fonline."
OL,18,FHow will the UK social media ban for
OL,19,Funder-16s work and which apps are
OL,20,Faffected?
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,330,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F329A1781799074
OL,3,CTeachers and pupils react to under-16s
OL,4,Csocial media ban
OL,6,FIsla Cauldwell, also in Year 10, said:
OL,7,F"I was surprised, because, we use
OL,8,Fsocial media without realising it. In
OL,9,Fschool we use a lot of YouTube to be
OL,10,Fable to understand concepts that might
OL,11,Fbe difficult to explain.
OL,13,F"It's a difficult situation, because
OL,14,Fyoung people do struggle to protect
OL,15,Fthemselves on social media. We don't
OL,16,Funderstand necessarily, what's right
OL,17,Fto be looking at at our age.
OL,19,F"Measures do need to be put in place,
OL,20,Fbut sometimes these measures can be
OL,21,Frestrictive to other parts."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,330,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F329A1781799074
OL,3,CTeachers and pupils react to under-16s
OL,4,Csocial media ban
OL,6,FFelicity, a Year 8 student, said: "It
OL,7,Fcan be good, but part of it can be
OL,8,Fbad. Our generation has grown up with
OL,9,Fsocial media in our lives.
OL,11,F"Bullying happens online, so that will
OL,12,Fbe reduced. But will it reduce
OL,13,Fphysical bullying?
OL,15,F"I feel like some apps, I can see why
OL,16,Fthey want to ban them, but other apps
OL,17,FI think... maybe. But even if they put
OL,18,Fan age restriction on stuff, people
OL,19,Fwill find new apps to get new stuff."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,330,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F329A1781799074
OL,3,CTeachers and pupils react to under-16s
OL,4,Csocial media ban
OL,6,FThe headteacher of Queen Elizabeth
OL,7,FGrammar School, David Marchant,
OL,8,Fwelcomed the Government's plans with
OL,9,Freservations.
OL,11,FMr Marchant said: "It's probably a
OL,12,Flong time coming. It's good to see
OL,13,Fthat the Government is planning to
OL,14,Flegislate on what is seen as concerns
OL,15,Fin society.
OL,17,F"I think traditionally there's been a
OL,18,Flot of pressure on schools to try and
OL,19,Fpolice these matters for themselves,
OL,20,Fso it's really good to have absolute
OL,21,Fclear guidance from the Government.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,330,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F329A1781799074
OL,3,CTeachers and pupils react to under-16s
OL,4,Csocial media ban
OL,6,FHowever, the teacher expressed concern
OL,7,Fover how the ban will look in practice.
OL,9,FHe said: "My worry is it will drive
OL,10,Fyoung people to darker corners that
OL,11,Fare harder to see, harder to legislate
OL,12,Fagainst, harder to understand what it
OL,13,Fis they're actually doing and
OL,14,Ftherefore increase the safeguarding
OL,15,Fchallenges instead of decreasing them."
OL,17,FThe MP for Whitehaven and Workington,
OL,18,FJosh MacAlister MP, first brought
OL,19,Fproposals before Parliament in
OL,20,FSeptember 2024, calling for stronger
OL,21,Fprotections for children online.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,330,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F329A1781799074
OL,3,CTeachers and pupils react to under-16s
OL,4,Csocial media ban
OL,6,FFollowing the Government's
OL,7,Fannouncement of the ban for under-16s,
OL,8,Fthe MP said: "Technology brings
OL,9,Fenormous opportunities, but childhood
OL,10,Fshould not be dictated by business
OL,11,Fmodels designed to maximise attention
OL,12,Fand keep children scrolling for as
OL,13,Flong as possible.
OL,15,FThe MP, who is the Minister for
OL,16,FChildren and Families, added: "These
OL,17,Fchanges will help give children their
OL,18,Fchildhood back and give parents
OL,19,Fgreater confidence that their children
OL,20,Fare being protected online."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,330,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F329A1781799074
OL,3,CTeachers and pupils react to under-16s
OL,4,Csocial media ban
OL,6,FOne of the first parents to start
OL,7,Fcampaigning for such a ban was Julie
OL,8,FCrooks, a Cumbrian mother of a child
OL,9,Fwho committed suicide.
OL,11,FFollowing the Prime Minister's
OL,12,Fannouncement, she said: "I think it's
OL,13,Famazing, I think it's the best thing
OL,14,Fever.
OL,16,F"I'm over the moon - now let's see how
OL,17,Fthey bring it in."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
